title: SPECIAL FRIEND...
description:
Suppose you have the misfortune of your son 

revealing he is homosexual and decides to 

bring his very 'special friend' to meet you 

and your wife.




I guess in this clip almost all 'normal' guys 

feel identified with the poor father struggling 

to be polite about the whole (unpleasant) thing.




Please seed because I can seed only for a short 

time. Thank you.
